Convict

The dataset contains details for convicts transported to Australia in the 18th and 19th centuries.

World War I

The dataset contains information and photographs of Queensland troops appearing in the weekly newspaper The Queenslander during the South African (Boer) War 1899-1902.

Mining Accidents

The dataset contains information about mining accidents published annually in the Queensland Legislative Assembly Votes and Proceedings from 1882 to 1945.
